; NAME:
;       GAUSSSCL
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;       This is a utility routine to perform a gaussian gray-level pixel
;       transformation stretch on a image.
;
; AUTHOR:
;
;       FANNING SOFTWARE CONSULTING
;       David Fanning, Ph.D.
;       1645 Sheely Drive
;       Fort Collins, CO 80526 USA
;       Phone: 970-221-0438
